phrases: Why did I do something that embarrassing?
I do not want to go to school tomorrow!
I am having a little identity crisis right now.
The people who yap about identities all the time
are usually the ones with no identity.
Like something that changes so easily could really be an identity, anyway.
Komachi-chan, why are you talking like that?
Also, you are making a weird face.
Well, I do not know what happened, but...
As if that twisted personality of yours is going to straighten out now.
But I kind of like you that way.
Oh, I would give myself a ton of points for that one!
I like me this way, too.
I would give myself a ton of points for that one!
My Teen Romantic Comedy SNAFU TOO!
Could you tell me when and where the meeting is?
Can it wait until Yuigahama gets here?
There is no reason to say it twice.
Um, Yuigahama-san, could you move away a bit?
We are ready to go, Iroha-chan!
It sounds as though the situation is not good.
At any rate, just be ready.
I am Tamanawa from Kaihin General High School...
It is worse than I expected.
Well, for starters, let us think of something we can do.
Looks like you have completed your assignment.
We did not have a modern Japanese assignment...
Well, let us hear what you wanted to ask me.
So you are starting with the budget, huh?
You guys do not seem to know what Christmas is all about.
I will show you what it is about.
I won them at a wedding after-party.
You can go by yourself twice!
If she went there alone four times,
she would end up enjoying it so much, she would pay to go a fifth time!
Worst case, I could even get stuck going with her the sixth time!
Seriously, someone please marry her already!
I will give you these, so go do some research.
It will also give you a break from
Why do we have to go now, when it is so damn crowded?
We can see Pan-san's Bamboo Fight!
I do not see the need to go during a busy season...
But it will be all decorated for Christmas now, will not it?
The Bamboo Fight is part of the park's regular annual operations.
Emphasis is placed on the world depicted by the attraction, not on the season.
You know a lot about it.
That much qualifies as common knowledge.
I really want to go with you, Yukinon.
You know, the way things have been with us lately...
They will probably have Pan-san merchandise in Christmas versions.
I kind of want to get something like that as a gift for Komachi.
Let us all pick something for her!
If that is the case, I guess we will have to go.
So wait, is it going to be the four of us?
so there will be one ticket leftover.
Oh, then we should invite one more!
Who are you planning to invite?
It is not right to just take Iroha-chan's side all the time!
I have had it rough, being stuck in the middle!
Has her soul been sucked out of her body?
Do not take pictures without asking.
But if I would asked, you would both have said no.
That does not mean you can take them without permission.
There will not be a next time.
There is nothing particularly Christmasy about this ride.
I do not see how it will help us.
What am I going to do?
I do not handle these things well, you know?
Looks like Tobecchi's having a tough time.
Why do not you help him out?
How does Tobe x Hachi sound?!
Let us ride it together, Tobe.
Listen, I am sorry about what happened before.
Is that the reason things have been awkward with you guys?
That had nothing to do with it.
They are all such nice people.
It is just because of the crowd...
Actually, there is nothing Christmasy about this, either...
Off you go to the world of Bamboo Fight!
We are not allowed to talk among ourselves?
Pan-san's eyes are not cute at all, are they?
I would rather look at Merry-chan the Precocious Cat.
I think this is really cute!
Isshiki's just trying to make herself look cute by saying Pan-san is cute.
C'mon, that is irritating and cute and annoying and embarrassing!
What would you like to have, Hikki-kun?
I do not really want anything...
I cannot believe people want to come here during this season.
I would rather never do it again.
I want to come here again.
You can come here whenever you want.
That is not what I meant...
But I will not wait for someone it is pointless to wait for.
Instead of waiting, I will make the first move.
Hey, coming to Land during this season is one thing, but...
I wonder what that newer place next to it is like.
Well, guess I should pick something.
Which one do you think Komachi-san would like?
You really do not have to get that serious about it...
Now that we have come this far, it will be faster just to ride it.
They might be waiting at the exit.
Does this kind of ride bother you?
It is not that it bothers me, really...
No, you do not handle these well, right?
I told you, I am fine.
It is nothing to get stubborn about.
I was not very confident about doing this,
but when I rode with Yuigahama-san, it was not a problem.
It is not going to drop yet.
You do not have to hold the bar.
You really do not handle these things well, do you?
Well, a long time ago, my sister...
It was when we were little.
When we came to places like this, she would always mess with me.
I think I can picture that.
And she really seemed to be enjoying herself.
I would not feel right taking money from someone who is sick.
But it does not work that way...
Ambulances do not make you pay, do they?
Emergency rescue personnel receive appropriate pay...
Something like this has happened before, has not it?
The prize that employee got for us.
We ran into my sister after that.
Everything you said about her was right, even then.
It was just what came to mind when I saw her.
Besides, even when people see through her, she does not try to put up a front.
I think that is one of her strong points.
She is always been loved by many people.
People said I was a good, quiet girl who did not because any trouble,
but I know that behind my back,
they also said I was unfriendly and unlikable.
People said the same thing about me.
In your case, would not they say you were impudent, conceited, and a piece of trash?
That last one did not really fit, did it?
But I did not know how I was expected to behave.
Still thinking you want to be like her?
I do not think that so much right now.
But she does have something that I do not.
I just ask myself why I do not have it.
You have something that I do not.
We were never the least bit similar.
I think that is why I wanted something different.
I realized that there was nothing I could do,
so I started to want something you and my sister did not have.
I thought if I had that, I could be saved.
Sorry for going ahead without you!
More importantly, did you take pictures of the parade?
I got some of Pan-san, too!
May I check over the data?
Um, if you would said something, we could have gone there.
Wha Tobe, what are you doing?
Brings back memories, does not it?
10 The Thing That the Light in Each of Their Hands Shines On.
Let it be said that of all who give gifts,
They should have talked it over more as a couple.
I dare you to say that again!
I mean, please say it again.
